name: #1 Pinky & Her Team
description:
My first doll was named Pinky. She came with her team which was very strange. There are also many that are like germs and demons. They are soft and cute and are perfect to be your friends.

My doll always comes in my dreams. And finally, I saw them jumping around in the room. In the near morning run they will disappear. Who will be the next one and what can she do? Wait to follow.
